Merge pull request #23 from tbekolay/set_translator

Use Sphinx.set_translator

Use Sphinx.set_translator.

This allows us to always register the `HTMLTranslator` instead of
informing users to add the translator to their configuration files.
The `html_translator_class` config option was recently deprecated,
so now seems a good time to switch.

Updaating field-list to not use a table layout.

This commit updates method, class, param field list domains to no longer
use a table but instead use dt/dl elements. This allows for massively
long strings in these values without wonky table alignment issues.
